{"tid":1000094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去年45名警員涉案被捕　較前年升5成半","createTime":"2019-01-29T07:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T08:45:48.000Z","uid":38172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81d131c58c590c2e7b012c48cf6d24803b707e91","tid":1000094,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"立法會保安事務委員會討論去年本港治安情況，公民黨議員楊岳橋關注去年警務人員被捕數字，又質疑警隊成立的誠信委員會成效，警務處處長盧偉聰表示，去年有45名正規警務人員涉案被捕，比前年上升5成半。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰表示，一直不會姑息任何違法違紀的人員，會公平公正和嚴肅跟進所有案件，他說，由副處長管理和督導的誠信委員會，以教育、管理、懲治和更生的方法處理有關問題，最近推出《不恰當行為介入指引》提醒管理人員，避免同事干犯罪行。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰表示，每個案件有多種成因，可能由於個人貪心、不恰當性慾望和同輩影響等引起，目前難以就誠信委員會是否有成效下結論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1440500-20190129.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1440500-20190129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=0ef20191\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1440500-20190129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d8eeac63\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1440500-20190129.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9b8dd2fd0c0c54cf5a8477cf124f1ddbb667fb3c","tid":1000094,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"本港去年整體罪案54225宗　自1974年來最低<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰表示，去年本港治安情況持續改善，整體罪案54225宗，較前年下跌3.2%，是自1974年以來最低，每10萬人計有728宗罪案，為1970年以來最低，但整體破案率為46.5%，按年下跌1.7%。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰在立法會保安事務委員會匯報去年治安情況時指，大部分罪案類別數字錄得下跌，包括行劫、爆竊、盜竊和強姦等，升幅最多的5項包括詐騙、扒竊、勒索、虐兒和兇殺案。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰提到，去年詐騙案有8372宗，按年升幅18.1%，其中電話騙案數字和損失金額都下跌，但社交媒體騙案、網上商業騙案、電郵騙案和投資騙案都有顯著上升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1440498-20190129.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1440498-20190129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=9382f415\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1440498-20190129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=778b7fc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1440498-20190129.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9b54c0605a39722b8c3f8b8d9ba0b3d2d673884b","tid":1000094,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"全港最大..."},{"pid":"cb5baf09f9192ef8109648a931ba188fa0170fac","tid":1000094,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"邱班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32e6713088d64f0dae6339aa646bcd234c49f25","tid":1000094,"uid":78141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"阿sir犯法唔使你教!"},{"pid":"01305b2648c6f9632aeb0b144063c948301e5a19","tid":1000094,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:57:36.000Z","msg":"呀sir 被捕唔洗你教"},{"pid":"87c303fea9cb866a3c0c8617b00a6c8ee8eacb90","tid":1000094,"uid":167928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"屯門青山警署軍裝巡邏小隊33005樊甘星"},{"pid":"8ffb7f69d0d10d04fae215c37e37d8b88285fa8f","tid":1000094,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"一個都嫌少"},{"pid":"50ac5bcb0c8877d5655a52bdf2b95830af116403","tid":1000094,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"所有同大陸人有關嘅罪案全部唔立案，放得走嘅放走，罪案率即刻低晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4215394c4fa28b6062c43ec807f3c082104ec4fa","tid":1000094,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:06:41.000Z","msg":"佔中影響警員犯法"},{"pid":"6e73d0620bd8e46c3add87a580ac0f2e93424040","tid":1000094,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"